Approximations
--------------

  * Arial / Calibri are not freely shipped with TeX Live.  The theme
    approximates them with Helvetica (`helvet`) or Calibri-clone
    (`carlito`).
  * Logo placement reads the PowerPoint placeholder geometry but
    approximates it within LaTeX's text-flow model; expect
    millimetre-level drift from the PowerPoint original.

If any of the above conflicts with the brand guidelines of
<INSTITUTION>, please open an issue at the repository where you
obtained this theme; the asset can be removed.
